## Prerequisites

### Required Tools
- SBT installed and configured
- Git repository initialized
- GitHub CLI (`gh`) for CI monitoring
- Internet access for Maven Central lookups

### Pre-Upgrade Checklist
- [ ] Current Scala version identified
- [ ] Build files located (`build.sbt`, `project/BuildSettings.scala`, `project/Dependencies.scala`)
- [ ] Java version compatible (Scala 2.13.18 requires Java 8+, Java 11+ recommended)
- [ ] Key dependencies identified (Play JSON, compiler plugins)
- [ ] Test suite runs successfully on current version

---

## Phase 1: Build Configuration Updates

### Step 1: Update Scala Version

**Location:** `project/BuildSettings.scala`

```scala
// Before
val buildScalaVersion = "2.13.10"  // or "2.13.12"

// After
val buildScalaVersion = "2.13.18"
```

### Step 2: Update Compiler Plugins

**Location:** `project/BuildSettings.scala` or `project/LibsPool.scala`

```scala
// Kind Projector
val kindProjector = compilerPlugin(
  "org.typelevel" %% "kind-projector" % "0.13.3" cross CrossVersion.full
)

// Silencer (if used)
val silencerVersion = "1.7.16"  // or latest compatible
```

**Location:** `project/plugins.sbt`

```scala
// WartRemover
addSbtPlugin("org.wartremover" % "sbt-wartremover" % "3.1.6")  // or latest compatible

// WartRemover Contrib (if used)
addSbtPlugin("org.wartremover" % "sbt-wartremover-contrib" % "3.1.6")
```

### Step 3: Handle SemanticDB

**⚠️ Critical:** Scala 2.13+ has built-in SemanticDB support. Do NOT use external `semanticdb-scalac` plugin.

**Location:** `build.sbt`

```scala
// ❌ WRONG - Do NOT add external semanticdb-scalac
// ThisBuild / dependencyOverrides += "org.scalameta" % "semanticdb-scalac_2.13.18" % "4.14.5"

// ✅ CORRECT - Use built-in SemanticDB
ThisBuild / semanticdbEnabled := true
ThisBuild / semanticdbVersion := "4.9.3"  // or latest compatible

// Exclude external semanticdb-scalac if any plugin pulls it in
ThisBuild / excludeDependencies ++= Seq(
  ExclusionRule(organization = "org.scalameta", name = "semanticdb-scalac")
)
```

### Step 4: Java 17 Compatibility (if needed)

**Location:** `build.sbt`

```scala
// Force Groovy version for AWS SDK compatibility
ThisBuild / dependencyOverrides ++= Seq(
  "org.codehaus.groovy" % "groovy" % "3.0.20"
)
```

