## Phase 4: Testing & Validation

```bash
sbt clean compile
sbt clean test
sbt undeclaredCompileDependenciesTest unusedCompileDependenciesTest
sbt scalafmtCheck
sbt assembly  # Test locally before CI!
```

---

## Phase 5: CI/CD Considerations

**Assembly Conflicts:** Use custom merge strategy (Phase 2, Step 5). Test `sbt assembly` locally first.

**Monitoring:** `gh pr checks --watch`

---

## Phase 6: Post-Upgrade Validation

- [ ] All compilation errors fixed
- [ ] All tests passing
- [ ] Zero implicit type warnings (or suppressed)
- [ ] Dependency checks clean
- [ ] Linters pass
- [ ] Assembly succeeds locally (if applicable)
- [ ] CI/CD green

---

## Common Issues & Solutions

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Plugin not found for target version | Use binary-compatible version (e.g., `kind-projector_2.13`) |
| Transitive dependency conflicts | Add `dependencyOverrides`, `excludeDependencies`, merge strategy |
| Compilation failures | Fix incrementally per Phase 3 |
| Test failures | Update assertions for Play JSON error format changes |
| CI/CD failure | Test assembly locally first |

